== Ibihembo ==

* Umuhoza yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi byimivugo harimo Kigali vibrate hamwe nubusizi, amarushanwa yishuri rya AEGIS
* Mu 2015 yitabiriye ubukangurambaga ku isi bwiswe abakobwa kuri perezida aho yari ahagarariye abakobwa bo mu Rwanda
* Muri 2018 yatsindiye kandi amarushanwa yateguwe na forumu ya demokarasi ya Afrika kurwego rwumugabane wa Afrika<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/lifestyle/home-decor-uplifting-girls-womans-pursuit?fbclid=IwAR14AW1NgOdZOPf95qgOrtcJy7HW3eD_B8-WDbR201wbuL09X9P8VcLlmLI</ref><ref>https://www.globalpeacechain.org/team_members/amina-umuhoza/</ref>

